# CSS Cache-Bust Version

When editing `public/styles.css`, also update the stylesheet cache-bust query string in `src/Frontend.elm`.

Current pattern:

```elm
node "link" [ Attr.rel "stylesheet", Attr.href "/styles.css?v=1" ] []
```

If `public/styles.css` changes, increment the `v=` value so browsers fetch the new stylesheet after deploy.

Examples:

```elm
-- Before
Attr.href "/styles.css?v=1"

-- After a CSS change
Attr.href "/styles.css?v=2"
```
